The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks for object detection and recognition in underwater videos, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper may fall under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of remote underwater video stations, which may fall under the information retrieval (cs.IR) category.
